Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说 你跟鲁鲁修发展的怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是学校公认的一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经接过吻了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只不过是活动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还什么都没做呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着害羞 大家都知道你喜欢鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 连维蕾塔老师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜欢他吗 喜欢到为了包庇他而向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都得堆满笑容与向自己开枪的女人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不戴着身为教师的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉·费列特 你真有胆量敢向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鲁鲁是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害死父亲的仇人


Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自过去的刺客


Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑门关已经陷落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澳门的空军设施也已经镇压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萨克斯坦的守卫任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把朝比奈和洪古调过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建业的内政就交由水无濑和杉山负责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来进行得很顺利呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不过是那些不肯接受我们的地方军阀 在各地举兵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够统一地方军阀的帅印 已经被哥哥率先得到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看池袋的情况 等我回来再继续帮你的功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔老师是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲是黑骑士团的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妮娜呢?会长呢?利瓦尔呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的就只有学校吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么娜娜会成总督?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么是真什么是假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}普通快车将迟到10分钟到达3号站台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}最先前往大久保方向的普通列车将从2号站台发车…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 作为初期准备已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就按这个样式继续作业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}现在向各位顾客发布优惠活动的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}现在 期间限定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然叫我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修呢 在约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做G列车的测试去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛 你为什么倒戈了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不同 既然是教团派来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哥哥和我之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B7报告司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼拜堂附近发现可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B5和B9已经前去确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是问鲁鲁修在哪里就有如此行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿…为什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象正在前往俱乐部会所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B2 B8被除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播报校内广播 让别的学生远离对象区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在向各位在校同学发布紧急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要靠近俱乐部会所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有报告说看到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到万不得已 我不想杀女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也尽量想避免无谓的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜大概是某种比喻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他们是这样坚信着的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢 神明什么的根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有什么背后长着翅膀的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是长胡子老人这样的神存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他会用什么GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说对手是小孩 也不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不愧是大名鼎鼎的科奈莉娅皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你的伯父 我也为你感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“既然存在着让人互相争斗的神明 还是干脆杀掉的好”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏了裸露的身体部分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手方位没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会阻止你!为了鲁鲁修大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不错的攻防体术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对我 杰雷米亚·哥德巴尔德却是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺你的时间!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子 趁我把这家伙定住的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…我的GEASS被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对停止的结界被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛·兰佩洛奇 果然已经被笼络了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么GEASS会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样我才会作为教团的刺客被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是来杀哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔!?你也被鲁鲁修笼络了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修现在正在池袋的车站大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 杰雷米亚卿 快把我解放出来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把朱雀君叫了出来 但该说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 鲁鲁也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 你想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是朱雀约她出来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦尔说鲁鲁修一直待在日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机情局的报告也证明他是清白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 为什么我还是不相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔 你打算背叛哥哥吗? 还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鲁鲁修取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我守着就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鲁鲁修会合的话应该能夹击杰雷米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得跟朱雀君说才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁是ZERO 是害死父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是分界线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界和贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总有一天我要让分界线消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果他们俩是共犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让11区变回日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 两人以前就是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子 明明大家都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我 放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 我不放!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…我已经不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 以前也发生过相同的事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们想抓住亚瑟的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实发生过那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次拉你起来的都是朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修在上面的话 两个人早就掉下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个体力白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要这么说的话 在掉下去之前就可以救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在笑什么 鲁鲁修是把尤菲给…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 鲁鲁 是一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚往你那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是教团的刺客 我的GEASS对他无效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还活着?刺客是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 总之我到达之前不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 朱雀在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像是朋友打来的电话啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的哦 朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该先办我的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你们俩约好见面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等等吗? 我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里将会成为战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夏莉的安全着想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朱雀在一起应该是最佳选择…


Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杰雷米亚·哥德巴尔德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有防弹措施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了鲁鲁修的GEASS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止GEASS对他无效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有解除的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着火了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖袭击!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 有本事就上来吧 Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的要事是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜欢鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀讨厌他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…曾喜欢过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你们俩以前感情这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么事是不能原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是朱雀没有原谅他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想原谅他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就已经原谅他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要联络消防局吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是先向军方优先报告的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Knight of Seven 枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…真是冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有可能是恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我来指挥周围的警备和消防事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想请你保护她的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 现在还是会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没叫上我的会议 谁去管它这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自ZERO的紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 我是扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急事件是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果担心台湾人的话 现在正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成了平民的疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进到车里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Knight of Seven大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你孤身一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你从我手心上逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁 一个人在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械身体 外加GEASS Canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的执着可不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orange君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是执着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是忠义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那狗皇帝有何为他鞠躬尽瘁的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这性能 果然用了Sakuradite啊

Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gefion Disturber

Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你功课做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这干扰Sakuradite的系统完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使环状线内的都市机能完全瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 能使东京静止下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 你是个很好的实验品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢鲁鲁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教团的位置 以及V.V.身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该全盘托出的 是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有 理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽忠到底的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要确认事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 不可能还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修啊 你为何要披上ZERO的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与祖国布里塔尼亚以及亲生父亲为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我是鲁鲁修·V·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生父布里塔尼亚皇帝对母亲见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此还导致娜娜莉双目失明双腿瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还夺去了我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也在事发现场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的首次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为敬爱的玛丽安娜皇妃的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却没能保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能尽忠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才成立了纯血派的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为ZERO 果然是为了玛丽安娜大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来杀我的 而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主君不是V.V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是 玛丽安娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来 我就毫无牵挂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚·哥德巴尔德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没完成尽忠的使命呢 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊 毕竟是我唯一的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是鲁鲁同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 让我也加入你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想守护鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮鲁鲁夺回属于他的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连妹妹娜娜也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我让杰雷米亚先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会为我清除障碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和他发生冲突 已经是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做出这种事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能和你说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是最后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就找医生 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恢复记忆时 感觉很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚假的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去记忆的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉全世界都在监视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁是单身在这样的世界作战的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 只有我才能给鲁鲁一个真实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管知道 爸爸也是被你牵扯进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你却怎么也恨不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然鲁鲁让我忘记了发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我又喜欢上了鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管记忆被人篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又喜欢上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管转世投胎几次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还是会喜欢上鲁鲁的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死 别死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…可以的吧 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是转世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能喜欢上你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上你…很多次…很多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 夏莉

Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,过去C.C.曾对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Geass是王的力量 会让你变得孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莉 我一直很想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你被我的Geass卷入混乱 最后成为了牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底该如何赎罪才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 告诉我吧…
